entries.title_d: Remain in the Dantooine system and transfer the data to a command shuttle. Insurgent needs that information immediately in order to continue his investigation.
entries.title: Dantooine System: Deliver the Clues
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the arrival location and wait for the the shuttle.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dantooine system and travel to the navigation waypoint supplied to you. This will take you to the shuttle's arrival location.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the shuttle and transfer the data. Once you have completed this task report to your superior.
entries.hello_d: Stand by, pilot. We will be ready to begin the transfer shortly.
entries.found_loc_d: Proceed to this location to make the dropoff to a command shuttle.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Beginning docking procedure now. Stand by.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: We have the information. We will return this to command immediately. Oh, and that Insurgent guy wanted to speak with you.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Wait at this location for the arrival of the lambda shuttle.
